<paragraph id="5BF29A10BE6C5E8725CD140F5722794A" pageId="0" pageNumber="89">Malaysia: (Peninsular) Perak, Pahang, and Selangor States; (Bornean) Sarawak (Bintulu Division) and Sabah (Pensiangan) States. Indonesia: Sumatra, Bengkulu Province; (Borneo) West Kalimantan Province (Mount Bawang).</paragraph>
